With evil surrounding her on all sides, Skye is at a crossroads. When the choices she makes can end entire universes, what is she going to do with every path before her leading to destruction? How will Skye come out on top in a world that corrupts those who hold the most power? Will she take it on herself to run this town under her own influence? Don’t miss the shocking next issue is Skye’s cross-universal journey!
